guide: 7You will passively get progress
7in this by just having a pet
7equipped all time. Even a
7Level 100 pet works for this.
7Use Enchanted Sugar that you get from
7killing pests in The Garden or from
7farming some Sugar Cane to brew
7Speed Potions (you will also need
7some nether warts for Awkward Potions first)
7Mine 50 Iron in the Gold Mine
7to unlock Iron Minions. Then buy
7Iron from the Mine Merchant in The Hub
7and Iron Forger in the Gold Mine and
7craft as many minions as you can.
7Give them the best fuel and storage you
7have access to and don't forget Auto Smelters.
7Remember to collect in time.
7To help with this, try to make bigger crafts
7by hand for Carpentry levels.
7Also do your daily experiments and make sure
7to have a pet active at all times
7(any pet works, even level 100).
7Save your coins from Meiser and ideally
7you get a score of 270+ in your run for
7High Score! You may need more coins than
7250k if you do drop rarer loot.
7Remember you can open chests at Croesus
7in the Dungeon Hub up to 48h after the run.
7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
7on owocato's, xMeru's or prtl's island.
7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End
7and hold it while some Ender Armor and/or Equipment.
7You will get passive progress for this
7while going for other goals. If you want
7to specifically go for this, use a
7Cobblestone Generator on your island.
7Unlock Skeleton Minions by killing skeletons you
7run into along your way. Then buy
7Bones from the Adventurer in The Hub
7and craft as many minions as you can.
7Give them the best fuel and storage you
7have access to.
7Remember to collect in time.
7You will most likely get this from
7leveling up skills.
7Remember to actually put the money
7you get in the Bank :)
7Wear armor enchanted with Growth 5
7(Enchanting Level 5), preferably Ender Armor
7while you're in The End or Mushroom Armor
7during the night.
7Applying Growth 5 costs 50 Levels each.
7If you still struggle, reforge your
7armor to Titanic.
7You will need Mining 12 for this as you
7need to enter the Dwarven Mines for this.
7Remember that Glacite Walkers take more
7damage from pickaxes.
7This requires Catacombs Level 1 and
7a completion of the previous floor.
7You may need help from party finder
7or friends for this.
7To get easy progress in this do
7contests like Wheat, Potato, Carrot
7or Mushroom as those are easy
7Bronze or Silver Medals to get.
7Optimal tool:
7Golden Axe with Efficiency 5
7Reforges: Double-Bit or Lush
7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood
7Forage in the Hub.
7Place as many minions as you can,
7give them a medium storage and the best fuel
7you can. Collect them in time.

24.description: 7Get Bronze or higher in a contest
guide: 7For this you will need Farming 10.
7Your best options for this will probably be
7Wheat/Potato/Carrot in the Garden or Mushroom
7if you use an Efficiency 5 Silk Touch Gold Axe
7in the Desert.
7Buy a Dirt Bottle (100k) from the Smithmonger
7in the Hub and reforge a weapon with it.
74Make sure to NOT shift-click it out
74of the menu after applying!
7You will get some progress for this
7by working on other goals.
7The easiest to go for are:
7Mushroom, Oak Wood, Bone,
7Sand, Wheat, Iron and Seeds.
7Reforge your Void Sword to Sharp
7at the Blacksmith in the Hub,
7or enchant any weapon with Critical 5
7(costs 50 Levels).
7For this you will need Combat 15 and
7completion of the previous floor.
7Going for this with your friends is
7probably the best option or you
7could use party finder.
7Get the common Rock from mining
72.5k Ores and hand it to Kat in The Hub
7(takes a day and 100k coins) or mine
75k more Ores to get the uncommon Rock.
7Remember to equip it!
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold, Diamond, Mushroom
7and Leaflet Armor. Grind Glacite Armor
7for the goal I've got Chills!
7and equip them all in one lobby.
7Hit 10 Endermen in The End
7so they follow you, then kill them
7all as quickly as you can.
7You most likely want to use Ender Armor
7and a Void Sword for this.
7Do 3 Tier 1 Revenant Horror Bosses
7and claim the rewards by talking to Maddox.
7nNo eggs:r
7Bingo, Endermen, Grandma Wolf, Armadillo,
7Squid, Guardian, Bee, Dolphin, Reindeer,
7Rock, Tarantula, Owl and Zoo
7nEggs:r
7Jerry, Silverfish, Pig, Rabbit, Endermite and Bat
7If you do eggs you will need 2.5k Chicken Collection
7and you'll want a Chicken Minion that can create more
7Enchanted Eggs for you once you put your first one in.
7Once you acquire a Void Sword and a decent
7armor like Ender or Glacite this should be
7fairly easy to do. You might get a little
7progress in this from doing the Slayer Goal.

7You will gain progress on this by going for
7the Iron Collector goal. Doing Mining Commissions
7will be a good help with this.
7Craft some easy minions while also getting
7those that will help with this Bingo.
7Mine Pure Iron in the Dwarven Mines
7with a Fortune 3+ pickaxe.
7You might want to use as many minions
7as you have access to for this.
7Remember to put a compactor in the minions
7when you plan on leaving for a while.
7Don't forget to fuel the minions,
7give them storages and collect them in time.
7You will most likely get this from leveling up
7skills for the Skill Average goal.
7Remember to actually put the money
7you get in the Bank :)
7Get yourself a splash, equip a Bingo Pet
7and get the cake buff by eating the cakes
7on skyerzz's, nightlibra's or prtl's island.
7If this doesn't finish it, get a Void Sword (200k) in the End
7and hold it while some Ender Armor and/or Equipment.
7You can unlock 17/17 Farming Collections,
76/11 Combat Collections, 6/6 Foraging Collections,
714/22 Mining Collections for a total of 43 collections.
7You will also get some Fishing Collections.
7Carrots and potatoes from killing
7Zombies in graveyard do count.
7Reforge your Void Sword to Sharp
7at the Blacksmith in the Hub or
7enchant any weapon with Critical 5 (50 Levels).
7This requires Catacombs Level 1 and
7a completion of the previous floor.
7You may need help from party finder
7or friends for this.
7You will get some progress in this by going for
7the Ink Sac Collector, Is This Safe? and
7Friend Of The Seas goal.
7Use the best fishing rod, bait and armor that you
7have access to and fish in The Park during rain.
7Recommended is a Chum Rod with Angler Armor and Dark/Fish Bait.
7Make sure to have Looting 3+ applied to your
7weapon and rod.
7You can also use fishing minions to help with this.
7Remember to give them the best fuel and storage
7you have access to and collect in time.
7To help with this, try to make bigger crafts
7by hand for Carpentry levels.
7Also do your daily experiments and make sure
7to have a pet active at all times
7(any pet works, even level 100).
7This unlocks at 5k Diamond Collection. Use Pure Ores
7in the Dwarven Mines for this. Craft it with
71 Enchanted Diamond and 8 Vines (costs 40 Jungle Leaves,
7requires Jungle Wood Collection 4 to unlock it in /trades.)
7Mine normal or Pure Ores in the Dwarven Mines.
7You will gain passive progress in this if you
7manual the Gold Collector Goal.
7Use the best fishing rod, bait and armor that you
7have access to and fish in The Park during rain.
7Recommended is a Chum Rod with Angler Armor and Dark/Fish Bait.
7Make sure to have Looting 3+ applied to your
7weapon and rod. You might want to use the Squid Head too.
7You should use SkyHanni's Trapper features
7to make this easier. Use /warp trapper
7to get back to Trevor whenever you want.
7You will need a bow for this.
7Fish with an Enchanted Chum Rod in the Rain
7in the Park. Use the best bait you can.
7Craft Leather, Iron, Gold and Diamond Armor
7Collect Ender Armor from The End (8 pieces including equipment)
7Craft Leaflet, Farm Suit, Mushroom and Cactus Armor
7Buy Squire, Rosetta's, Celeste and Starlight Armor from Rosetta
7Wear armor enchanted with Growth 5
7(Enchanting Level 5), preferably Ender Armor
7while you're in The End or Mushroom Armor
7during the night.
7Applying Growth 5 costs 50 Levels each.
7If you still struggle, reforge your
7armor to Titanic.
7Throw Goblin Eggs that you get from killing Goblins
7or opening chests in the Crystal Hollows
7in the Dwarven Mines and kill what spawns from it.
7Some HOTM perks, such as Sky Mall, Efficient Miner,
7Luck of the Cave, Mining Speed and Anomalous Desires
7may be helpful for this.
7Do commissions and events in The Dwarven Mines,
7claim your daily powder from the Puzzler and
7from giving Fetchur the items he asks for.
7Fetchurs items are all listed in the Wiki.
7Try to do those while a '2x Powder' event is active.
7You might want to use the Royal Reforge on your
7equipment to gain more powder from events.
7Optimal tool:
7Golden Axe with Efficiency 5
7Reforges: Lumberjack's or Moil
7Get Haste 3 from a splash to instamine wood
7Save all the Chum you gather from the other
7fishing goals and fill 8 Chum Buckets with it.
7In total you will need 90 Glowing Mushrooms
7and 16k coins to buy this from Moby on the Desert Island.
7You will most likely get this passively.
7Use /be ingame to view your progress once you
7talked to Bramass Beastslayer in The Spiders Den.
7fNo eggs:
7Dolphin, Bee, Grandma Wolf, Bingo, Rock, Owl,
7Enderman, Tarantula and Oringo pets
7fEggs needed:
7Jerry, Rabbit, Pig, Chicken, Bat, Silverfish
7To get the Enchanted Eggs needed, kill Chickens
7in The Barn till you get the Chicken Head recipe.
7Once you get your first Enchanted Egg, put it into
7one Chicken Minion to generate more of those over time.
7Kill mobs with a weapon that you have
7Scavenger 3+ applied to.
7You will gain passive progress in this
7by having a pet equipped at all times.
7Even a Lvl 100 pet counts for this.
7You should use SkyHanni's Trapper features
7to make this easier. Use /warp trapper
7to get back to Trevor whenever you want.
7You will need a bow for this.
7Visit the Campfire in The Park and do
7the Trial of Fire. (140 dps over 10s)
7You will need 160 Dark Oak and 1k Spruce
7in the progress of this.
7Enchant your Ender Armor with Growth 5
7and if you still struggle, reforge it
7to Titanic at the Blacksmith.
7You can also use the Wand of Healing.
7Talk to Jax in the Hub
7under the Weaponsmith
7and complete on of his challenges.
7You should buy an Artisanal Shortbow
7for this.
7You should either kill Endermen in
7End using your Void Sword (200k) and
7Ender Armor for this (buy the Ender Training
7Perk from Tyzzo next to the Draconic Altar)
7or Spiders in the Spiders Den with a Cleave 5
7weapon. You might want to also use the free
7Combat XP from Bestiary Miletones for this.
7Can be made from Lapis Lazuli Collection 5 (10k),
7a drop from fishing, from the Experimentation Table,
7and dropped from Ender Nodes in the End (11-13% chance).
7Kill Team Treasurite members in the Crystal Hollows.
7They spawn in the Mithril Deposits and you will need
7Heart of the Mountain 4 to go there.
7Wear Ender Armor enchanted with Growth 5
7and wear it in The End.
7You can also enchant Mushroom Armor like that
7and wear it in The Garden.
7Growth 5 requires Enchanting Level 5
7and costs 50 Experience Levels per piece.
7Reforge your armor to Titanic if needed.
7Brew a Speed Potion by using either Enchanted Sugar
7or an Enchanted Sugar Cane. If you use the Sugar, you'll
7need to combine the brewed potion with a Glowstone.
7You can get that Glowstone by buying one block
7from the Builder and breaking it on your island.
7You can get the Enchanted Sugar (Cane) from farming
7Sugar Cane or killing pests in the Garden.
7Kill Sheeps in the Desert Island (/warp desert)
7place as many Sheep Minions as you can and
7give them the best fuel and storage you have
7access to. Remember to collect them in time.
7Talk to Guildford in the Dungeon Hub
7and complete 4/4 objectives for 3 races.
7Don't forget to talk to Guildford
7after each run you do.
7Grab the Fairy Souls you run across while
7doing this Bingo. You can use NEU (/neusouls on)
7or TimeDeo's Tutorials on YouTube for help.
7Kill mobs with a weapon that you have
7Scavenger 3+ applied to.
7For this you should utilize the Garden.
7Melons will unlock at Garden Level 6.
7Use the Gardening Axe and its upgrade once you
7unlock Melons. You might want to save some copper
7to enchant the axe with Sunder.
7You will most likely get this passively.
7Talk to Bramass Beastslayer in The Spiders Den.
7Use /be ingame to view your progress once you did that.
7You can unlock 17/17 Farming Collections,
76/11 Combat Collections, 6/6 Foraging Collections,
714/22 Mining Collections for a total of 43 collections.
7You will also get some Fishing Collections.
7Do commissions and events in The Dwarven Mines,
7claim your daily powder from the Puzzler and
7from giving Fetchur the items he asks for.
7Fetchurs items are all listed in the Wiki.
7Try to do those while a '2x Powder' event is active.
7You might want to use the Royal Reforge on your
7equipment to gain more powder from events.
7You can also fish up and kill Mithril Grubbers
7in the Abandoned Quarry (Fishing 6).
7Recommended for this either Revenant Horror II
7or Tarantula Broodfather II. Use your Ender Armor
7and Void Sword (200k) for this.
7To progress in this you can:
7- Participate in Dragon Fights
7- Salvage Ender Pieces at the Draconic Altar
7- Kill Lost Adventurers
7- Collect secrets in dungeons
7This unlocks at 5k Diamond Collection. Use Pure Ores
7in the Dwarven Mines for this. Craft it with
71 Enchanted Diamond and 8 Vines (costs 40 Jungle Leaves,
7requires Jungle Wood Collection 4 to unlock it in /trades.)
7fNo eggs:
7Dolphin, Bee, Grandma Wolf, Bingo, Rock, Owl,
7Enderman, Tarantula and Oringo pets
7fEggs needed:
7Jerry, Rabbit, Pig, Chicken, Bat, Silverfish
7To get the Enchanted Eggs needed, kill Chickens
7in The Barn till you get the Chicken Head recipe.
7Once you get your first Enchanted Egg, put it into
7one Chicken Minion to generate more of those over time.
7You will most likely get this from leveling up
7skills for the Skill Average goal.
7Remember to actually put the money
7you get in the Bank :)
7Use the wiki to figure out what Fetchur asks for.
7You will need to get into Dwarven Mines to be
7able to even talk to him.
7For this you'll want to open structure chests
7in the Crystal Hollows, do a Nucleus Run
7(you will need a Small Gemstone Sack for this to count)
7or kill Worms/Scathas.
7For this you need to place down a Chum Bucket
7while fishing. It's recommended to use a Chum Rod
7as this will gain quicker progress.
7Purchase it from Moby on the Desert Island.
7cDon't forget to actually deposit the Chum you fish ;)
